Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:16.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.18,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:24.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:34.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:37.58,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:44.32,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:47.39,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:50.72,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.05,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:57.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:02.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:06.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:10.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.35,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:17.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:21.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:24.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:30.71,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:38.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有尽头的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:16.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不见的羽翼引导
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遥远的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:24.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不见的未来依旧在等待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:34.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不愿清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:37.58,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:44.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包围 谁也逃不出这个圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:47.39,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:50.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变幻不定的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:52.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:57.00,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.39,0:01:00.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:02.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:06.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方听闻的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:10.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震动鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.35,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:17.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:21.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我渐渐清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:24.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:30.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:34.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的伤口 是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:38.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因为你和Burst The Gravity
